title: SPY Presents: Big City, Tiny Altercations
description: We didn't have any big wigs, so we went with some little wigs instead, picking-up a handful of "little people" who were down for a few rounds of boxing. From the moment the bell first rung, our diminutive homeboys were throwing blows Rock 'em Sock 'em Robots-style, taking it to the streets, to the beach and even spilling the action over to the steps of a nearby hotel.
